Parameters:
world - the world to which this diagnosis applies

factoryName - the type of diagnosis to be created
secondDoc - the doctor to ask a second opinion from (if needed)
args - the arguments to the creation of the new diagnosis
Throws:
NoOpenedPatientFileException - the creating doctor has no patient file opened
PatientIsDischargedException - the patient this diagnosis applies to is not checked in
NotAFactoryException - an invalid type of diagnosis was given
WrongArgumentListException - somehow the list of arguments used to create the diagnosis was wrong
ArgumentNotAnsweredException - the given argument was not answered
ArgumentConstraintException - the given argument was incorrect
ArgumentIsNullException - the given argument was null
